648
00:40:48,070 --> 00:40:50,322
Aku sangat senang sampai serasa itu mimpi.

649
00:40:50,906 --> 00:40:53,117
Apa maksudmu, Psikopat?

650
00:40:56,412 --> 00:40:58,622
Siapa kau?

651
