666
00:42:06,649 --> 00:42:08,526
Dia tahu kau menulis lagu.

667
00:42:11,403 --> 00:42:12,446
<i>Su-a tersayang.</i>

668
00:42:13,822 --> 00:42:14,657
<i>Su-a,</i>

669
00:42:15,241 --> 00:42:18,702
<i>aku menyukai lagu-lagu karyamu</i>

670
00:42:19,370 --> 00:42:23,415
<i>karena aku selalu bisa merasakan</i>
<i>kehangatan dan harapan darinya.</i>

671
00:42:24,667 --> 00:42:28,796
Aku baru tahu dia merasa seperti ini.

672
